; Coverage for amount.cc lines 494-495:
; When multiplying a bare amount (no commodity) by a commoditized amount,
; the result inherits the commodity from the multiplier. Here 2.0 has
; no commodity, and amount has $, so the result gets $.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $50.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format "%(2.0 * amount)\n"
$100.00
$-100.00
end test
